title: Grateful Dead Live at Rich Stadium on 1986-07-04
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, Dupree's Diamond Blues, CC Rider, Tennessee Jed, My Brother Esau, Touch Of Gray

Set 2

Cold Rain & Snow-> Fire On The Mountain-> Samson & Delilah*-> The Wheel*-> I Need A Miracle*-> Uncle John's Band-> Drums-> Gimme Some Lovin'-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: U.S. Blues

*Broadcast on TV for Farm Aid. Dylan, Petty & Heartbreakers Opened.
